title: What's happened to Kendall Jenner? Supermodel isn't her usual fashionable self as she sports grillz and oversized knitwear
text:
What's happened to Kendall Jenner? Supermodel isn't her usual fashionable self as she sports grillz and oversized knitwear The supermodel sported an unusual look as she partied at a London nightclub Share Kendall Jenner isn't as stylish as usual (Photo: Splash) Share Get celebs   
Kendall Jenner is usually effortlessly-stylish. 
But the supermodel showed off a bit of an odd look as she went out partying in London on Monday night. 
The Keeping Up With The Kardashians star is in town for London Fashion Week and headed out to make the most of her trip across the pond. 
The 21-year-old was spotted on a night out with pals, including fellow model Lily Donaldson, at the city's Cirque Le Soir Night Club - but she wasn't her usual fashionable self. Read More Braless Kendall Jenner shows off serious underboob while modelling her and Kylie's bizarre new clothing collection Kendall Jenner headed out to Cirque Le Soir nightclub (Photo: Splash News) 
Kendall was wearing an off-white mini dress and black ankle boots with an odd over-sized knitted poncho over the top. 
The woolly creation - a Burberry couture cape - boasted two large baubles that hung down in front of her and a thick hood that she had pulled up on her head to cover her hair. 
It might keep her warm while she's waiting for a taxi, but it might be a bit much for inside the club. 
Her shiny brunette locks were pulled back in a pony tail and almost completely hidden underneath the hood. Grillz isn't her best look ever (Photo: Splash News) 
That's not the strangest thing about her new look though. 
Kendall's make-up wasn't as natural as it usually is, with heavy eyeshadow and bright red lipstick. 
Her jewellery is a little over the top as well, with big gold hoop earrings hanging from her lobes. 
But perhaps the strangest thing of all is the grillz she's wearing in her mouth. She's in town for London Fashion Week (Photo: Splash News) Video Loading Click to play Tap to play The video will start in 8 Cancel Play now
